{"tid":1802344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發現一個好有意義的眾籌一直無被關注","createTime":"2019-12-29T11:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T12:10:09.000Z","uid":62506,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5a2343a5ebed5e8387bbc172754f63175a7aa603","tid":1802344,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"我唔識搞手<br />\n<br />\n但我睇個眾籌非常有意義，對爭取國際社會支持香港人爭取民主好有積極作用<br />\n<br />\n但個眾籌進展一直好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家一齊幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾籌網址 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/free-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Ffree-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition%2F&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9zUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=369e9d2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/free-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition/</a><br />\n<br />\n各位手足，我哋係Free Hong Kong Exhibition團隊，由一班海外香港人組成，主要打國際戰線。我哋希望以巡迴展覧嘅形式，將香港人嘅聲音帶到海外。作為响城牆外面生活嘅人，我哋自覺有責任將港共政府嘅所作所為話俾全世界知。响西方民主社會，人民就係力量，政府嘅決策同立法往往都以民意為依歸，而展覽正正可以提供一個空間同平台，直接同市民接觸交流。我哋希望以普羅大眾為出發點，提高民間對香港事態嘅關注，團結國際民運陣線，希望响國際間有更加多迴響，間接向港共政府施壓。<br />\n<br />\n由九月開始，我哋已經先後响德國三個城市自資舉辦咗三次展覽同一次講座，亦協辦咗一個sharing session，近期亦同其他歐洲城市聯絡緊，希望將展覽帶到更多地方，遍地開花，與更多外國人接觸，團結國際力量。經過三次展覽之後，我們團隊經已山窮水盡，所以希望透過眾籌籌集經費，繼續 [和你展]。下一階段我們打算到比利時、丹麥，我哋亦已同烏克蘭當地聯絡，希望响寒冬凜烈嘅十二月或一月直達基輔，同五年前烏克蘭革命人民接觸，連結國際民運陣線。<br />\n<br />\n我哋今次眾籌目標係三萬歐元，折合大約為港幣二十六萬五千元，用作未來幾個月再舉辦展覧同講座嘅開支。巡迴展覧結束之後如有任何剩餘資金，將會全數捐贈星火同盟。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位手足可以幫忙，課一課金，亦可以幫忙share，感謝大家。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n我哋團隊facebook page :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Free-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFree-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239%2F&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9zUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=55409a67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Free-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxVhzFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwxVhzFS.jpg&h=94f011dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZVmgTJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZVmgTJ.jpg&h=a5c03ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qo5EN0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQo5EN0q.jpg&h=2314032e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6J1XzFs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6J1XzFs.jpg&h=a2b5f3f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"027d0c91f183d4f3925420e4aa535dcf0bb1e448","tid":1802344,"uid":310970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"尋日已經課左少少～"},{"pid":"c579374d8bc2b9c4d7a536253b8d03645a063a0a","tid":1802344,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13f5d82972023d447b1d90f79a4ee8521daae87","tid":1802344,"uid":70685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:03:19.000Z","msg":"1.1港島見"},{"pid":"b4b75a2fe1fe95800ae5032d13dbdace9184fe76","tid":1802344,"uid":70685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:03:39.000Z","msg":"1.1港島見"},{"pid":"398da9b9fbd198766789bb4dda7a90da9e91459f","tid":1802344,"uid":70685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"1.1港島見"},{"pid":"7dd54c9cc327bba150a7a36e56bde99e23708d44","tid":1802344,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fabb4c6c231d47ddc6d0404abf9b10047e03d97","tid":1802344,"uid":68261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply